CLI program for learning commands and words. The program will reward you if you
answer question right and fast. Then it will not ask the same question for a
while. So it gives you spaced repetition.

You need a questions.txt file in the format: question###answer

First line in your questions file will be used for stats. Leave it empty

My questions file are just for personal backout. You better use your own.


You need python 3

EULA: You are not allowed to use this software with proprietary OS.  So no
Windows, no MacOS, no other capitalist shit. If you break this rule I own your
house, car, wife, and children. All yours belongs to me.  

